(2, 'welcome_associate', 'This template is used when new associate is created.', 'Welcome Letter', '<p>Welcome to Leica Biosystems!</p>\r\n<p>It\'s going to be a great year and we are excited to have you join Leica Biosystems and be part of our team.</p>\r\n<p>Your first day will be on {start_date} and reporting to {manager_name}, {manager_title}.</p>\r\n<p>We are a Danaher Company.  We believe our associates are our best asset and as we say here \"The Best Team Win\", regardless of whether you will be dealing directly with customers or providing support to those associates who do.</p>\r\n<p>It is our associates who uphold our Mission - Advancing Cancer Diagnostics, Improving Lives and our Vision24 - enabling patients to receive their diagnosis within 24 hours from biopsy. No other company is positioned to streamline the whole process.  We truly have an impact on improving lives.  We are so excited that you joined us in our journey.</p>\r\n<p>Below is a link to your New Associate Packet.  Please review all the documents.  All documents requiring your signature will need to be submitted.  Your timeliness on signing the forms will help to make your onboarding process a success.</p>\r\n<p>Again, welcome to the Team and we are so excited about your decision to join Leica Biosystems!  All of us extend a warm welcome to you and wish you the best of success at Leica!</p>\r\n<p>If you have questions prior to the start date, please contact me at <a href=\"http://lbsnew-opss.leicabio.com/nap2/admin_masters/email_template/update_email_template/847-405-5457\">847-405-5457</a> or send me an email at <a href=\"mailto:alina.waity@leicabiosystems.com\">alina.waity@leicabiosystems.com</a>.  We look forward to having you come onboard.</p>\r\n<p>You can login on {welcome_url} with <strong>username</strong> : {user_name} and <strong>password</strong> : 123456.<br><br></p>\r\n<p>Note: Please use below password for protected documents.<br>Password: <strong>Leica@123</strong>.</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>Best Regards,</p>\r\n<p><strong>Alina Waity <br></strong>Sr. Coordinator <strong>|</strong> Human Resources<strong> | <span xss=removed>Leica Biosystems</span> |<br></strong>1700 Leider Lane<br>Buffalo Grove, IL 60089<br><a href=\"Call: +1.847.405.5457\">T: +1.847.405.5457</a><br><a href=\"Call: +847.714.2422\">M: +1.847.714.2422</a><br><span class=\"baec5a81-e4d6-4674-97f3-e9220f0136c1\">Email: </span><a href=\"mailto:alina.waity@leicabiosystems.com\">alina.waity@leicabiosystems.com</a><br>Web: <a href=\"https://www.leicabiosystems.com/\">https://www.leicabiosystems.com/</a></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"http://nap.bluenettech.com/assets/img/signature.jpg\" alt=\"Signature Logo\" width=\"404\" height=\"89\"></p>\r\n<p>This message (including any attachments) may contain confidential and/or proprietary information that should be read only by certain individuals. As a result, any unauthorized disclosure, copying, or distribution of this e-mail and the information contained herein is strictly prohibited and may constitute a violation of law. If you are not the intended recipient, please notify us by email by replying to the sender and delete this message. The sender disclaims that the content of this email constitutes an offer to enter into, or the acceptance of, any agreement; provided that the foregoing does not invalidate the binding effect of any digital or other electronic reproduction of a manual signature that is included in any attachment.</p>', '2019-09-12 00:41:11'),
